OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,FMusic producer and lifelong Coventry
OL,8,FCity fan Pete Waterman says he regrets
OL,9,Fnot buying the club when he had the
OL,10,Fchance now he has seen his team
OL,11,Fpromoted back to the Premier League.
OL,13,FThe Sky Blues needed just a point
OL,14,Fagainst Blackburn Rovers on Friday
OL,15,Fevening to confirm their spot in the
OL,16,Ftop flight next season - but it was
OL,17,Ffar from easy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
