PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,FFrank Lampard's men found themselves a
OL,8,Fgoal behind in the second half, but
OL,9,Fwith just minutes or normal time
OL,10,Fremaining, Bobby Thomas headed home to
OL,11,Fequalise and secure the draw, sending
OL,12,Fthe travelling fans wild.
OL,14,FA special parade and party will take
OL,15,Fplace in May to celebrate their
OL,16,Fpromotion back to the top flight,
OL,17,Fwhich is for for the first time in 25
OL,18,Fyears.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,FMr Waterman told ITV News Central he
OL,8,Fused to live next to the ground when
OL,9,Fhe was young. He was delighted with
OL,10,Fthe result and feels it will be a
OL,11,Fmassive boost to the city.
OL,13,FHe said: "Sitting in your lounge, you
OL,14,Fcan be a bit more relaxed than the
OL,15,Ffans at the ground. I thought it was
OL,16,Fpretty predictable.
OL,18,F"You have to take you hat off to Frank
OL,19,F(Lampard). The management of the game,
OL,20,Fthe last two games, has been superb.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,F"He's got a goal, hoe's not going to
OL,8,Fcompromise that goal and you could see
OL,9,Fthat. It was a point. We've got to get
OL,10,Fthe point. Never mind the title, we'll
OL,11,Fdeal with that next few days, but now
OL,12,Fwe've got to get that point and you
OL,13,Fsaw that.
OL,15,F"That's management of a high degree,
OL,16,Fbecause your fans are all wanting you
OL,17,Fto win, but the bottom line is, you've
OL,18,Fgot to get that point.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,F"I thought Blackburn played a great
OL,8,Fgame. They needed a point as well as
OL,9,Fwe did. I thought in the last five
OL,10,Fminutes the referee should have just
OL,11,Fblown his whistle and we could have
OL,12,Fall gone and just got drunk."
OL,14,FIt's been a tough few years for Sky
OL,15,FBlues fans, with relegations, points
OL,16,Fdeductions and even being forced out
OL,17,Fof their home ground.
OL,19,FThings are now back on track though,
OL,20,Fthe club is back at its home ground
OL,21,Fand is on the up.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,FMr Waterman said: "I go back to 1950s
OL,8,Fwhen I used to take bikes in for the
OL,9,Ffans for a sixpence because I lived
OL,10,Fnext door to the football ground for
OL,11,Ftwenty five years.
OL,13,F"Coventry has been a rollercoaster,
OL,14,FI'm just so happy for all those fans,
OL,15,Fthe stadium and the stability. I was
OL,16,Fsad when Mark Robins went because he's
OL,17,Fa friend from my Walsall days, but
OL,18,FDoug (King) made a great decision, a
OL,19,Fbrave decision."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,FMr Waterman believes it's a real boost
OL,8,Ffor the city of Coventry, but for him
OL,9,Fpersonally, is there a tinge of regret?
OL,11,FHe said: "What it means to me, I wish
OL,12,FI'd bought the city when I had the
OL,13,Fchance to buy it.
OL,15,F"I had the chance to buy it, I didn't
OL,16,Fand the next year they went into the
OL,17,FPremier League and got a balloon
OL,18,Fpayment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,F"I look at it and think it's great for
OL,8,Fthe city. The city needs this, it
OL,9,Freally, really does. We're getting a
OL,10,Fnew town centre, all my old shops are
OL,11,Fbeing pulled down and it's a new start
OL,12,Ffor the city, which is fantastic news."
OL,14,FCelebrations took place in Coventry
OL,15,Fimmediately after the Blackburn game
OL,16,Fas well the following day in the city
OL,17,Fcentre. A bus parade and a one-day
OL,18,Fmusic festival has also been planned
OL,19,Ffor Monday, May 4.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,FMr Waterman also planned to have his
OL,8,Fown party with his grandson who had
OL,9,Fjust come back from Mexico.
OL,11,FHe said: "He doesn't take his Coventry
OL,12,FCity kit off at all. So the whole time
OL,13,Fof his ten days in Mexico he's had
OL,14,Fpeople coming up to him saying you're
OL,15,Fgoing to get promoted.
OL,17,F"So it's going to be a good day and
OL,18,Fwe'll have a drink for the lads."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,FThe Sky Blues will be up their with
OL,8,Fthe country's biggest teams including
OL,9,Fthe likes Manchester City, Aston
OL,10,FVilla, Arsenal and Chelsea.
OL,12,FBut it's an old favourite that Mr
OL,13,FWaterman is looking forward to seeing
OL,14,Fmost next season.
OL,16,FHe said: "Oh, Manchester United of
OL,17,Fcourse. There's nothing like it. I
OL,18,Flive on the red side of Manchester, so
OL,19,Ffor your home team to come and play at
OL,20,Fthat team and if you beat them, then
OL,21,Fthat's a bonus isn't it."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776687067
OL,3,CMusic mogul Pete Waterman wishes he
OL,4,Cbought Coventry City when he had the
OL,5,Cchance
OL,7,FCoventry City need one more win to be
OL,8,Fguaranteed to be Champions of the EFL
OL,9,FChampionship.
OL,11,FMr Waterman had one more message for
OL,12,Fthe fans looking ahead to next season.
OL,14,FHe said: "I really think this is the
OL,15,Fstart of a really exciting era for the
OL,16,Fcity. Grab it with both hands guys and
OL,17,Fenjoy every minute of it.
OL,19,F"It will be a rollercoaster, but do
OL,20,Fyou know what, rollercoasters are
OL,21,Fexciting."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
